net.sf.freecol.common.option

Class MapGeneratorOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.freecol.common.option.MapGeneratorOptions

  • public class MapGeneratorOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Keeps track of the available map generator options. More of a handy place to organize the names than an actual option type.
    See Also:
    MapGenerator, OptionGroup
